Class PlainGroup

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.goinstant.auth.PlainGroup
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Group, Comparable<Group>

    public class PlainGroup
extends Object
implements Group, Comparable<Group>
    A Plain Group implementation. Implements Comparable so it can be inserted into TreeSets. Fields have protected visibility to allow easy subclassing.
